{"tid":1469380,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不分化嘅精髓","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:56:31.000Z","uid":188758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9686912d79cdf011e67c8e9470add7887be7a945","tid":1469380,"uid":188758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:37:52.000Z","msg":"所謂現場事 現場決定<br />\n和理非 勇武 不分化嘅精髓係前線做咩都好<br />\n都支持 做文宣做宣傳 將壓力減到最底<br />\n<br />\n呢樣野係個運動行到而家嘅原因<br />\n<br />\n警察可以失控<br />\n點解要求示威者表現似聖人<br />\n<br />\n警察射嘅係香市民<br />\n示威者打嘅係搞事嘅公安 同 過期居留大陸記者<br />\n<br />\n唔該用番智慧去拆件事<br />\n唔係指摘 散播失敗<br />\n<br />\nDay 1 就係雞蛋<br />\nDay 1 就知係冇得打 但都要試<br />\n<br />\n香港人 無辦法<br />\n世界原來不像你預期<br />\n我地做人沖沖幾十年 <br />\n<br />\n盡做囉 對得住自己 對得住家人朋友<br />\n對得住下一代 自己知自己做緊正確嘅事就得<br />\n<br />\n共勉"},{"pid":"aa81fb4f9183647a6cbab57e2f847cb007257a89","tid":1469380,"uid":188758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:38:55.000Z","msg":"推一下先"},{"pid":"96fb4ba3e92e77db645379def5ebff3348ed0630","tid":1469380,"uid":188758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:40:29.000Z","msg":"推多下"},{"pid":"0252792c6e74abae8bdbddb1432ca82e2255b709","tid":1469380,"uid":188758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:41:42.000Z","msg":"推多一下"},{"pid":"b065798356a985f5efe0d5dcee32b4eb214c6003","tid":1469380,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:42:01.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"4e768d6d7b6cd3773c8d8367a84cf61ab3f5ffe4","tid":1469380,"uid":188758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:43:54.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"23f1a2b2480cdac794ad8318854654ff9d956987","tid":1469380,"uid":188758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:48:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"77b5307401a54b86a6637669d4082b43346b74